00:42:22.620 --> 00:42:27.699
control, if you click on that deploy to Netlify button, you can see that what it does is it

00:42:27.699 --> 00:42:33.100
allows you to take the same site that I'm showing you in my repository.

00:42:33.100 --> 00:42:36.860
You can then link it up to your Netlify account.

