00:50:55.699 --> 00:51:00.379
use GitHub throughout my workflow a little bit easier with blogged down.

00:51:00.379 --> 00:51:03.459
But with the other options, I think I go back and forth.

00:51:03.459 --> 00:51:07.899
I do tend to use Netlify more, but I wouldn't say it's a completely strong preference.

00:51:07.899 --> 00:51:12.419
So, Desiree, you seem like you can see more questions than I can.

00:51:12.419 --> 00:51:13.419
Yeah.

00:51:13.419 --> 00:51:14.419
I think I must be able to.

00:51:14.419 --> 00:51:15.419
I only see three.

00:51:15.419 --> 00:51:16.419
Okay.

00:51:16.419 --> 00:51:17.979
Here, yeah, this is very...

00:51:17.979 --> 00:51:18.979
Here's another question.

00:51:19.060 --> 00:51:23.580
I created index.rmd, but the tab build site does not appear.

00:51:23.580 --> 00:51:25.979
What do I have to do?

00:51:25.979 --> 00:51:27.860
Restart RStudio.

00:51:27.860 --> 00:51:33.699
So sometimes it might not yet detect all the files in there for it to identify that it

00:51:33.699 --> 00:51:37.100
needs to show you that build book or build site button.

00:51:37.100 --> 00:51:42.219
So restart RStudio, open that RProj file again, and you should see that populate.

00:51:42.219 --> 00:51:46.379
