00:51:46.379 --> 00:51:50.020
What does signing up to Netlify using a version control account...

00:51:50.020 --> 00:51:54.659
Why does signing up to Netlify using a version control account make your life easier?

00:51:54.659 --> 00:51:57.139
Makes your life easier if you use GitHub already.

00:51:57.139 --> 00:52:01.260
If you don't use GitHub already, then it may not make much of a difference to you.

00:52:01.260 --> 00:52:06.620
But the reason why I say that is because you can keep your files that are already in GitHub

00:52:06.620 --> 00:52:08.659
and have Netlify connect to those.

00:52:08.659 --> 00:52:14.260
So whenever you make a change locally on your computer to your website, you build your site

00:52:14.260 --> 00:52:19.219
locally, you can see it, you push to GitHub, and then that's all you have to remember to

00:52:19.219 --> 00:52:23.540
do is you just have to push it to GitHub, and you don't have to do any extra step to

00:52:23.540 --> 00:52:25.500
actually deploy or publish your site.

00:52:25.500 --> 00:52:29.379
So the way we showed you today in this webinar was a very manual way.

00:52:29.379 --> 00:52:33.459
It's not a bad way, but it's a very manual way of dragging and dropping physically that

00:52:33.459 --> 00:52:38.919
folder into Netlify to both deploy it the first time and to update it.

00:52:38.919 --> 00:52:41.939
And so that could wear on you after a bit if you're updating frequently.

00:52:41.939 --> 00:52:44.939
If you have a site that's just kind of done and you want to share it, then that's not

00:52:44.939 --> 00:52:46.300
really a big deal.

00:52:46.300 --> 00:52:51.739
But if you're updating and maybe adding materials every couple days or every week, you may want

00:52:51.739 --> 00:52:54.899
to think about starting to use version control.

00:52:54.899 --> 00:52:58.419
But we didn't want to necessarily depend on that for this workshop because we wanted to

00:52:58.419 --> 00:53:02.620
make sure that we optimized for being able to share on short notice, which for me does

00:53:02.620 --> 00:53:04.260
not involve GitHub.

00:53:04.260 --> 00:53:05.260
Agreed.

00:53:05.260 --> 00:53:09.139
Okay, here's another question.

00:53:09.139 --> 00:53:10.939
