00:53:10.939 --> 00:53:16.179
It is, what if I would prefer not to use Netlify but a university server to store my

00:53:16.179 --> 00:53:17.179
material?

00:53:17.179 --> 00:53:18.179
Oh, yeah.

00:53:18.179 --> 00:53:19.179
You can do that as well.

00:53:19.179 --> 00:53:20.620
